column2: Sunny- nice day- 1st nice day in 2 weeks.
Some algae- sunny- cool day.  Partly cloudy.
Nice sunny cool day.  Partly cloudy- 1-10 mph wind.
Partly cloudy- overcast and sunny- slight wind.
Last report for this year- sunny- beautiful calm day- 0-5 wind- clear.
Lots of rain-everyday- partly. cloudy- air temp 55- NE wind 5-10 mph.
Calm- hot day- getting ready to storm
Sunny- SW wind 0-5 mph- partly cloudy
Partly cloudy- sunny- NE wind 10-20mph- choppy- much rain and flooding
Rain made water muddy- some weed problems- nice sunny day with two rain showers
Clear- partly cloudy day.  0 - 5 mph.  Water is starting to clear.
Clear bright sunny day- last reading for '93.
Beautiful- cool- clear- moderate NW wind- no white caps- very nice day.
Beautiful fall day- sunny- partly cloudy- calm- the water level is down because of the flood several weeks ago- they are fixing the dam
We had a very tornado-like storm on 8/28/95 at 3 am- water at flood stage and very churned up and very brown.
Water is high- due to 3" of rain.  Cloudy- equipment is falling apart- rings on water sampler.
Water roiled due to two inches of rain in the last 2 days.
Cloudy- breeze from east.  Will rain soon.
Clear- bright.  Lots of rain and wind all last week.
Cloudy- E breeze 5 mph. slight rain last night. 3 loons by deep hole.
Southwest breeze at 5 mph- light rain- and a storm is moving in.
Clear sky- wind 12 mph NNW.  1 boat fishing.
Partly cloudy- wind 10 mph SW.  2 fishing boats.
Windy- sunny.  Saw 1 eagle.  1 fishing boat.
Sunny- light wind.  1 fishing boat- 2 loons.  60 deg.
Calm- overcast.  Humid.  1 fisherman- 5 geese and 2 loons.
Windy- cloudy and cold.  62 F.  1 fisherman.
It's a beautiful day.  Sunny and cool.  2 loons.  50 geese in wild rice.
Rain which we needed bad.  Cloudy and windy.
Cloudy- windy-  1 loon- 1 fish crane- 2 ducks.
Cloudy and overcast and cold.  1 loon.
Osprey on nest- 2 fishermen and 2 adult loons and 2 babies
cloudy- 2 fishermen- 2 loons- dog days- lake is green on shore
Cloudy and windy.  3 loons- 2 boaters- 2 fishermen.
2 osprey... 1 on nest- 1 in tree.  Geese.  1 fisherman.
2 osprey on nest. Geese with young - 2 fishermen- 1 boater tearing up lake - no respect for people fishing.
Overcast- cold (48 F) Osprey on nest- 1 fisherman.
Sunny breezy beautiful day.  1 fish crane- 2 fisherman- ospery on nest.
1 eagle- 1 loon.  cool clear sunny day.
One fisherman- one loon flying- two loons on the lake.  Geese.  Sunny and chilly.
Sunny- windy- 48 degrees.  2 loons and one fisherman on lake.
1 fisherman- one lady fishing off shore.  Weather cool and misty.
Weather hot and humid. 1 deer eating lily pads. 1 loon
sunny and calm- 2 ducks- 1 eagle and 3 swallows
1 osprey- 1 fisherman- partly sunny and cloudy
Very stained water. Algae bloom present. Warm- partly cloudy day.
Cloudy- cool- rained the night before- rivers running high- dark due to heavy cloud cover.
